Most of my folks are developers, so we don't have a whole lot of the web developers with JavaScript or HTML,

00:27:46.160 --> 00:27:49.160
which can really enhance some of those Shiny apps.

00:27:49.160 --> 00:27:55.160
So we're trying to pick some of that up so that we can make those applications a little bit more robust.

00:27:55.160 --> 00:27:56.160
That's great.

