00:57:59.159 --> 00:58:01.159
doing that right now.

00:58:01.159 --> 00:58:03.159
There's probably, depending on the contractors,

00:58:03.159 --> 00:58:07.159
they've got some spreadsheets out there where they're just tallying up

00:58:07.159 --> 00:58:13.159
individual, again, raters scoring on that company.

