00:58:16.159 --> 00:58:19.159
But nothing that's being done programmatically just because of those

00:58:19.159 --> 00:58:21.159
legal concerns.

00:58:21.159 --> 00:58:24.159
At least that's what I've been told in the past when I brought it up.

